  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“<strong>Slay the Spire</strong> Meets <strong>Into the Breach</strong>! Great New Deckbuilder Just Landed!”</i> - <strong>Haelian</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"One Of The Best Grid-Based Roguelike Deckbuilders I've Seen So Far\"</i> - <strong>Wanderbot</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"AWESOME Turn-Based Tactics Roguelike Deckbuilder!!\"</i> - <strong>Retromation</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/da8b1290b204e9350db9a40d22d3d825.avif?t=1762542073\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your heroes that will fight to rid this world of corrupted Tendryll.  In order to survive, your heroes must work together and coordinate their unique abilities.  You will encounter deadly enemies, dangerous traps, and perilous environmental hazards that hex your cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/fa341942bfb560d1d1ca7ffc1d374d90.poster.avif?t=1762542073\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/fa341942bfb560d1d1ca7ffc1d374d90.webm?t=1762542073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/ba0dbb39fdef21246aeba4a3ff145b09.avif?t=1762542073\" width=600 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each hero has its own move deck and draws a guaranteed move card each turn - allowing your heroes to always be in the fight. Dedicated map nodes let you swap in new move cards to maintain a balanced move deck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alongside their move decks, heroes also have unique attacks and skills that give them powerful ways to reposition themselves and others.  You will knock enemies back into walls, teleport to random locations to gain an energy advantage, or throw allies and enemies across the battlefield - dealing heavy damage around where they land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/f1b619590c135289ecd74af1df572fc5.avif?t=1762542073\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Double your block, gain Invisibility, or play your card twice - every card can potentially be improved with impactful runes like these.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you’re feeling bold or desperate, shops and black markets offer risky anomalies that reward you with items for free - if you don’t pay with your life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/6f06908cbc9fa97fcf672f2dc76b7024.avif?t=1762542073\" width=600 height=192 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/b431d5189a6c1100fd66b9679914a653.avif?t=1762542073\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival requires difficult choices.  Along your journey, your heroes will find card-altering runes, unique movement cards, and class-defining relics.  Will your heroes take the greedy path to perfect their archetypes, or will they take a safer path, restoring their health with the hope of surviving another battle?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/f4b7205260824b7f990ec955e330a45f.poster.avif?t=1762542073\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/f4b7205260824b7f990ec955e330a45f.webm?t=1762542073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 170+ cards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 115+ relics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3+ heroes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 acts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5+ bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 35+ unique encounters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 20+ combat modifiers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 30+ bounties that unlock heroes, relics, and potions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 14+ runes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 10 ascension levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Full Steam Deck support (pending Steam validation)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/6222ba76fed929be43a69c6d081a3daa.avif?t=1762542073\" width=600 height=108 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wishlist to get updated when we release. Every wishlist helps our development of the game! </p>",
