 card-altering runes, unique movement cards, and class-defining relics.  Will your heroes take the greedy path to perfect their archetypes, or will they take a safer path, restoring their health with the hope of surviving another battle?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/f4b7205260824b7f990ec955e330a45f.poster.avif?t=1762542073\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/f4b7205260824b7f990ec955e330a45f.webm?t=1762542073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 170+ cards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 115+ relics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3+ heroes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 acts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5+ bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 35+ unique encounters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 20+ combat modifiers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 30+ bounties that unlock heroes, relics, and potions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 14+ runes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 10 ascension levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Full Steam Deck support (pending Steam validation)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915780/extras/6222ba76fed929be43a69c6d081a3daa.avif?t=1762542073\" width=600 height=108 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wishlist to get updated when we release. Every wishlist helps our development of the game! </p>"